data.title: Saginaw Independent School District / EMS ISD Homepage
data.text:
EMS ISD Kicks Off New School Year with Enthusiastic Convocations

The events put a focus on the strength of the EMS ISD community and the shared goal of carrying the torch for all students.

Ribbon Cutting and Dedication Celebrates the Opening of Eagle Mountain High School

Close to 800 community members joined the celebration, which featured student performances, a dedication and a ribbon cutting ceremony.

Excited to be in EMS ISD!

EMS ISD welcomed new employees to the district with excitement and inspiration ahead of the new school year.

After Three Decades of Service to Public Education, Superintendent Chadwell Announces Retirement

The Board of Trustees now begins the search process for the next top leader of EMS ISD.
